cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.HC 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and machine learning (LG) techniques for facial correspondence. The paper also involves graphics (GR) and multimedia (MM) techniques for generating synthetic faces and processing video frames. Additionally, the paper discusses the human-computer interaction (HC) aspect of facial alignment. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.LG, followed by cs.GR, cs.MM, and cs.HC.
